        <td>Email inbox only — not stored in any database</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p>No other data is collected. MarketKit does not use analytics platforms (e.g. Google Analytics), advertising trackers, session recording tools, or any form of behavioural tracking.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
    <p>MarketKit does not set any first-party cookies for tracking or advertising purposes.</p>
    <p>The following minimal technical exposure exists:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> may set a security cookie (<code>__cf_bm</code>) as part of its bot management service. This is a technical necessity of using Cloudflare Pages hosting and is not used for advertising. It expires within 30 minutes of inactivity.</li>
      <li><strong>Browser localStorage</strong> is used (not cookies) to save your Settings tab preferences. This is not a cookie and is not shared with any third party.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>A cookie and tracking notice is displayed on your first visit to this site. By continuing to use the site after dismissing this notice, you acknowledge the minimal data exposure described in this policy.</p>
    <p>You may block third-party CDN requests using a browser extension such as uBlock Origin. Note that blocking Google Fonts will fall back to your system font, and blocking jsDelivr will disable the QR code generator.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Third-Party Services &amp; Their Privacy Policies</h2>
    <p>MarketKit relies on the following third-party services. Each has its own privacy policy which governs how they handle data from requests made when you visit this site:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages &amp; CDN</strong> — <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">policies.google.com/privacy</a></li>
      <li><strong>jsDelivr CDN</strong> — <a href="https://www.jsdelivr.com/terms/privacy-policy-jsdelivr-net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jsdelivr.com/terms/privacy-policy-jsdelivr-net</a></li>
      <li><strong>TinyURL</strong> (URL Shortener feature only) — <a href="https://tinyurl.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tinyurl.com/privacy</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Affiliate links on the <a href="/tools.html">Recommended Tools</a> page point to third-party websites. Once you leave MarketKit, the privacy policy of the destination website applies. MarketKit is not responsible for the privacy practices of linked third-party services.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Affiliate Links &amp; Tracking</h2>
    <p>Some links on this website are affiliate links marked with ★. When you click an affiliate link, you are directed to a third-party website. That third-party website may use cookies or tracking pixels to attribute the referral to MarketKit. This tracking occurs on their platform and is governed by their privacy policy — not this one.</p>
    <p>MarketKit does not receive any personally identifiable information about you as part of the affiliate relationship — only an anonymous commission notification if a qualifying purchase is made.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>MarketKit is not directed at children under the age of 13 and does not knowingly collect any personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information via this website, please contact <a href="mailto:hadi@eiilab.com">hadi@eiilab.com</a> and the information will be removed promptly.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>7. Your Rights (Singapore PDPA)</h2>
    <p>Under the Singapore Personal Data Protection Act 2012 (PDPA), you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access</strong> — request information about any personal data held about you</li>
      <li><strong>Correction</strong> — request correction of any inaccurate personal data</li>
      <li><strong>Withdrawal of consent</strong> — withdraw consent to collection or use of your personal data at any time</li>
      <li><strong>Data portability</strong> — request a copy of personal data you have provided in a portable format</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Given that MarketKit does not store personal data on its own servers, the only personal data that may be held is email correspondence. To exercise any of the above rights, please contact <a href="mailto:hadi@eiilab.com">hadi@eiilab.com</a>. Requests will be responded to within 30 days.</p>
    <p>For data held by Cloudflare, Google, jsDelivr, or TinyURL, you should exercise your rights directly with those organisations via their respective privacy policies linked above.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>8. International Visitors</h2>
    <p>MarketKit is operated from Singapore. If you access this website from outside Singapore, please be aware that your data (as processed by Cloudflare, Google, and other CDN providers) may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. By using this website, you consent to such transfers to the extent they are necessary for the Service to function.</p>
    <p>For visitors in the European Economic Area (EEA): Cloudflare and Google comply with GDPR requirements. Where applicable, their Standard Contractual Clauses or equivalent mechanisms apply to international transfers.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>9. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Server logs (Cloudflare)</strong> — retained per Cloudflare's standard log retention policy (typically up to 7 days for free tier logs)</li>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts request logs</strong> — retained per Google's log retention policy</li>
      <li><strong>Email correspondence</strong> — retained for as long as necessary to respond to your enquiry, then deleted or anonymised</li>
      <li><strong>localStorage (your device)</strong> — retained until you clear your browser data or revoke it manually</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>10. Security</h2>
    <p>This website is served over HTTPS via Cloudflare Pages with TLS encryption. No sensitive personal data is collected or stored by MarketKit. All tool inputs are processed locally in your browser and are never transmitted to MarketKit's servers (except as described in Section 2).</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. The effective date at the top of this page will be updated accordingly. We encourage you to review this page periodically. Continued use of the Service following any changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>12. Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy-related questions, requests, or concerns:</p>
    <p>Hadi Irwein<br>eiilab<br>Singapore<br><a href="mailto:hadi@eiilab.com">hadi@eiilab.com</a></p>
